Package org.jscsi.initiator

This package contains all the core classes to provide an easy and usable iSCSI (RFC 3720) initiator.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Configuration Configuration This class stores all informations, which are set during an iSCSI Session, Connection or are set as the default values.
Initiator Initiator This class represents an initiator, which request messages to a target defined by the iSCSI Protocol (RFC3720).
LinkFactory LinkFactory Implements a Factory which enables the Initiator to switch between multithreaded and singlethreaded modes.
 

Package org.jscsi.initiator Description

This package contains all the core classes to provide an easy and usable iSCSI (RFC 3720) initiator.
